  <brief_title>Addressing Dementia Via Agitation-Centered Evaluation</brief_title>
  <acronym>ADVANCE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of AXS-05 for the Treatment of Agitation in Subjects With Dementia of the Alzheimer's Type</official_title>
